Title: Hopf Structure in Nambu-Lie n-Algebras

Authors: A. E. Santana and R. Muradian

Comments: LaTeX, 6 pages, no figures

Journal-ref: Theor.Math.Phys. 114 (1998) 67-72

We give a definition and study Hopf structures in ternary (and n-ary)Nambu-Lie algebra. The fundamental concepts of 3-coalgebra, 3-bialgebra andHopf 3- algebra are introduced. Some examples of Hopf structures are analyzed.